Company Overview of Scrap Connection Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Scrap Connection Inc. operates an online platform for the scrap metal industry in the Netherlands and internationally. It allows scrap producers and consumers to sell and buy ferrous and non-ferrous scrap metals. The company was founded in 2010 and is based in Amsterdam, the Netherlands. It has locations in the United States and India.


Simon Carmiggeltstraat 6Amsterdam,  1011 DJNetherlandsFounded in 2010



Phone: 31 40 4913 3088

www.scrapconnection.com







