About
Scrap Connection Inc is located at the address 1024 Highway 90 E in Houma, Louisiana 70364.  They can be contacted via phone at (985) 868-0489 for pricing, hours and directions.  Scrap Connection Inc specializes in Trucks, Imports, Diesel.  Scrap Connection Inc has an annual sales volume of 501K - 999,999.  .Scrap Connection Inc provides Jump Starts, Inspections, Exhaust to it's customers.  For maps and directions to Scrap Connection Inc view the map to the right.  For reviews of Scrap Connection Inc see below.









